HEADWORD: genocide
<hw>gen"o*cide</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The systematic killing of a
racial or cultural group; <as>as, the Nazi <ex>genocide</ex> of Jews
left few in Germany or Poland after World War II</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> race murder, racial extermination.</syn>⟦br⟧
